# Trivy Vulnerability Allowlist
# This file contains CVEs that have been reviewed and accepted as acceptable risk
# Add entries here for false positives or vulnerabilities that are mitigated by other controls

# Dev-only dependencies (not used in production build)
# All vulnerabilities below are in dev dependencies or require breaking changes to fix

# Critical - vitest (dev dependency, test framework)
GHSA-5xrq-8626-4rwp  # vitest - arbitrary file read/execute in UI server, dev-only

# High - vite (dev dependency, build tool)
GHSA-fx2h-pf6j-xcff  # vite - path traversal bypass on Windows, dev-only

# Moderate - dev dependencies and transitive deps
GHSA-67mh-4wv8-2f99  # esbuild - CORS issue in dev server, not in production
GHSA-qx2v-qp2m-jg93  # postcss - XSS in CSS stringify, transitive in Next.js, awaiting upstream fix
GHSA-4w7w-66w2-5vf9  # vite - path traversal in optimized deps, dev-only
GHSA-v6wh-96g9-6wx3  # vite - NTLMv2 hash disclosure via UNC path, dev-only
